&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 clinical research nurse to join our Wexham park research team. We are looking for a motivated, skilful and knowledgeable nurse who works well as part of a team. Knowledge of research is favorable but not essential, full training will be provided. This is a great opportunity for anyone thinking about a career in clinical research. Newly qualified nurses are also encouraged to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
